raw_data.title: Executive Coach
raw_data.description: Provides consultation to executive level clients on innovative methodologies, tools and techniques to enable better management and assessment of an organization’s business functionality, management (both fiscal and personnel), operations, data and analytic capabilities.

raw_data.title: Senior/Lead Consultant
raw_data.description: Provides strategic consulting to identify and implement new ways of effectuating change management and enables better management and assessment of an organization’s business functionality, management (both fiscal and personnel), operations, data and analytic capabilities.

raw_data.title: Results Consultant/Facilitator I
raw_data.description: • Provide consulting to identify and implement an organization’s desired results. Utilizing interviews and organizational diagnostic tools to identify the specific barriers that may be impeding the organization’s achievement of those results. Identifying unique strengths and building a plan that utilizes these strengths to address any barriers and achieve the stated results. • Design and deliver workshops and retreats customized for an organization’s objectives and culture, utilizing a wide variety of frameworks or topics. The facilitator will develop appropriate agendas, deliver the session in accordance with the agenda, actively engage participants as appropriate, document/capture key discussion points and action items, and follow up with individuals/teams to ensure goals were satisfactorily met.  • Results Consultant/Facilitator I have supervisory roles, as applicable.
